\pard\plain\s0\qj\widctlpar\f0\fs20\sl240\slmult1 \fi0 { {Team click refers to the perception of peak team performance. Based on anecdote and evidence from psychology and anthropology, an individual\rquote s perception of team click should contain some or all of the following components: {\par
