\pard\plain\s0\qj\widctlpar\f0\fs20\sl240\slmult1 \fi0 As I explain in more detail in the next chapter (Chapter \~{\field{\*\fldinst{\lang1024 REF BMtheory \\* MERGEFORMAT }}{\fldrslt{?}}}), team click is a candidate concept for explaining the link between joint action and social bonding in group exercise contexts.\par
